Scenario name : Success login with valid data user

  Given the user opens WeMine or WeMineOffice
  Then the login page is displayed

  When the user inputs username with existing data
  Then the username field should accept the input

  When the user taps the Next or Continue button
  Then the app sends a request to "/user/who"

  When the request is successful
  Then the Microsoft login page is displayed with the password field

  When the user inputs a valid Microsoft password
  Then Microsoft successfully validates the credentials

  When the app sends a request to "/user/me"
  Then the app successfully retrieves the user profile

  When the app sends a request for the list of users
  Then the app successfully retrieves the list of users

  When the app fetches master data from each endpoint
  Then the progress bar updates for every endpoint processed

  When all master data has been downloaded
  Then the progress bar reaches 100% and shows "Complete"

  Then the app displays a prompt "Restart required to apply new master data"

  When the user restarts the application
  Then after restarting, the user is directed to the Dashboard or Home Screen
  And all master data is synchronized and ready to use
